dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Green County, Wisconsin in 2021 and includes the layers 'Green_Airport_2021,' 'Green_General_2021,' and 'Green_Shoreland_2021.' [General: County jurisdiction zoning combined with municipal zoning; boundaries.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://wi-greencounty.civicplus.com/179/Downloadable-GIS-Data-Forms
